+GET /api/bgpls/graph?protocol=isis  → { nodes: [...], links: [...] }
+```
+
+Render as D3 force-directed graph. Node color = router role (PE/P/RR). Edge thickness = IGP metric (inverse — lower metric = thicker edge). Edge label = adjacency SID.
